{# templates/api.html.twig #}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>All APIs</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>All working APIs</h1>

        <h2>Routes and their details:</h2>

        <p> - /api/ - shows an overview for all available APIs</p>

        <p> - /api/quote - shows a random quote with some date and time details</p>

            <li><a href="{{ path('quotes') }}">Quotes</a></li>

        <p> - /api/deck - shows you all cards sorted from a deck</p>

            <li><a href="{{ path('deck_sorted') }}">Sorted deck</a></li>

        <p> - /api/deck/shuffle - shuffles the deck and show you all the shuffled cards.</p>
        <p>A sessions is started when you shuffle the deck. If you are out of cards, shuffle again.</p>

        <form method="post" action="">
            <p>
                <input type="submit" name="shuffle" value="Shuffle"
                    onClick="this.form.action='{{ path('deck_shuffled') }}';"
                >
            </p>
        </form>

        <p> - /api/deck/draw - to draw a card from the deck. You can also see how many cards are left in the deck.</p>

        <form method="post" action="">
            <p>
                <input type="submit" name="draw" value="Draw one card"
                    onClick="this.form.action='{{ path('api_draw_a_card') }}';"
                >
            </p>
        </form>

        <p> - /api/deck/draw/:number - to draw a specific number of cards (more than 2). You can also see how many cards are left in the deck.</p>

        <form method="post" action="">
            <p>
                <input type="number" name="num" value="2" min="1" max="52">
                <input type="submit" name="draw" value="Draw cards"
                    onClick="this.form.action='{{ path('api_draw_some_cards', { num: 0 }) }}'.replace('0', this.form.num.value);"
                >
            </p>
        </form>

    </body>
</html>
